<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%#= image_tag attachments["#{@recipient.sign}.svg"].url %>Welcome to Horrorscope</h1>
    <p>
      Your email address <%= @recipient.address %> has been signed up to receive your daily horrorscope.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      You'll get the daily <%= @recipient.sign %> horrorscope, but head to <%= @url %> to check out what everyone else has to look forward to.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day! Try not to get eaten in your sleep by a giant rabid sloth!</p>
  </body>
</html>